name: Wangi & Uruh
description:
Wangi & Uruh (Introduction) 

Wangi and Gemuruh are two characters with extra ordinary power. They used their power to protect people in need. Wangi have excellent fighting skills and she can detect something related with supernatural energy. 

Uruh is a nick name, short from Gemuruh. His existence are pretty uniqe, he came and goes as he pleased like the wind. Somehow he have telepathic bond with Wangi, he said could be because their ancestors power crossed path longtime ago. Wangi always knew the presence of Uruh, because there's always sounds of thunder whenever Uruh is near. 

08:00 seconds animated drawings with audio
